2640,"uid":14521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T07:01:56.000Z","msg":"火影世界第一"},{"pid":"86faa6ed9b88ac077ae719dd92da22b050360b09","tid":82640,"uid":3711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T07:03:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>火影世界第一</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n海賊王世界第一"},{"pid":"effd781cf26791f4e12346c1bf21ee0784eabb80","tid":82640,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T07:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你話海賊拖我唔會反駁你，但至少佢個故事完整度高，每個角色都好平衡。<br />\n<br />\n反觀火影，天天失蹤，佐助大蛇丸突然洗白，港女櫻連配角都不如</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲要後期d畫亂9咁黎，求9其撚2野就話係螺旋丸，當年呢套野係笑話咁睇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年我直情睇唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n棄咗一段時間睇返 都係咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八尾出開始俾人屌到化啦，d人之後都係為左睇角色而睇，但幾年後既今日大把真心膠like呢套野，講出黎都俾人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28849ec83d27071580d29252b8540e668fd3993f","tid":82640,"uid":49216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Suckcomic/M.1219017495.A.F21.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FSuckcomic%2FM.1219017495.A.F21.html&d=g7k2Ncn0pY6isMlTzy50xUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=ea3af1e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Suckcomic/M.1219017495.A.F21.html</a><br />\n呢篇潮文當年笑左好耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌中晒point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有幾中pt呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一，話嗚人追住佐助唔放，唔理小櫻，好基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nJump一直都係「友情，熱血，勝利」做宗旨，佐助都問過好多次做咩死追住佢唔放，嗚人次次都答佢「因為係朋友」。<br />\n喱啲未友情囉，要睇追女就睇少女漫畫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二，小櫻做配角又點，本身個故事就係嗚人主角架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第三，話輪回眼樣衰唔吸引都算，人人睇法唔同。話寫輪眼屈機，卡卡西無血統都有新招。我知果時未講到，但宜家根本知道卡卡西隻眼既技其實係帶土練出黎啦。而且仲係六道遺傳落黎既，屈少少都唔過份啦。<br />\n<br />\n第四，嗚人n次修練。連載緊果時我都有屌過，次次練n集，用就用得果1，2次。但其實練既野之後都有佢既作用，如果一開始3年後就夠曉打未仲on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第五，話蠍果場好拖，係果期係咁。疾風傳之後係差左，但喱啲熱門漫畫係咁架啦，一定拖長打，無得避免架啵。<br />\n路飛打明哥唔拖咩？屌你，打打下差最後一野，同我講無mp 喇，幫我頂十分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結，都係果句，疾風傳前世界第一，後就比海賊王差少少。"},{"pid":"61477d4eddf8ac15baa42b006806bea8e1567b06","tid":82640,"uid":49216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T07:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老實講 兩套都拖劇情架喇<br />\n但要揀既話一定係海賊王<br />\n火影d劇情亂<span style=\"color: navy;\">到</span>仆街又悶<br />\n唔應該死個d人就死撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩叫唔應該死既人死晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打仗，做危險任務梗係有機會死先叫危險架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知有啲角色死得好唔抵，好可惜<br />\n但佢地唔係為死而死架嘛，佢地既死都可以令身邊既人成長。<br />\n<br />\n如果你話唔應該死既，艾斯未仲唔應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你，成個白胡子海賊團去救佢，打撚左幾廿集，死撚左幾百人，連老爹都死埋，結果未又係一拳比赤犬打死左。<br />\n<br />\n但艾斯既死，係牽起一個新時代嘛。<br />\n不過，之後又送返個剎波比路飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d425ccd1ff6005bba7f3d61e2e4d3e62e92174d","tid":82640,"uid":13938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:50:50.000Z","msg":"海賊王嘅情唔及火影"},{"pid":"9fc11ce1857f1da5267a79bdd0328e21436726a3","tid":82640,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解會有人簡火影 垃撚圾到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我睇過百幾集火影 最後頂唔順放棄咗<br />\n真係好撚悶<br />\n海賊王根本係動漫之王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好睇勁多 完全唔悶又勁好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n悶到暈囉"},{"pid":"1877b0fde6773212579f10a1c1eb30fb49e2a3b0","tid":82640,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"海賊王最on9既係路飛個人設係肉體變到幾強都好都係要做on9仔<br />\n修練兩年得實力成長，心靈仲係一個on9仔"},{"pid":"1e16beaf1fb355bfd902b1d1d1a973a88251684a","tid":82640,"uid":72257,"like":0,"dislike":