/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、朋友既叛逃離開 <br />\n去到萬人景仰、有個大波老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、成功拯救朋友<br />\n海賊係好好睇好好笑 但我鍾意火影個心路歷程多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eacbf341c5926bfc5717d73b7d9b000ba1c39e93","tid":82640,"uid":4402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯  路飛真係無一齊成長個種感覺<br />\n嗚人真係睇住佢成熟變真男人</blockquote><br />\n鳴人果種on9係細路嘅on9，大個左咪冇<br />\n路飛果種係本身就on9，幾多歲都改唔到㗎啦<br />\n你睇卡普就知路飛正經極有限，除非真係戥中佢認真位<br />\n有啲位笑下咪算你班人又要放到無限大黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger <br />\n睇住鳴人由小學雞慢慢成長到成為獨當一面既大人<br />\n個種感覺喺海賊係揾唔到 路飛既成長唔係唔好<br />\n而係鳴人更貼近現實 俾所有人排斥、做平胸女神隻兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、朋友既叛逃離開 <br />\n去到萬人景仰、有個大波老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、成功拯救朋友<br />\n海賊係好好睇好好笑 但我鍾意火影個心路歷程多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n完全同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇火影有時真係好有共鳴 描寫內心既感情真係寫到好足 海柒王我睇到魚人島已經棄撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  死神就更加唔好提"},{"pid":"e06c68a89afe3f3da0c53d8711eb7a00b4beb7da","tid":82640,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩大王道已經無睇好耐 死神當笑話仲過引<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人比較鐘意全職獵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhxh你都應該好耐無睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b472aba51374c1380153b7a70037ce09b043fb","tid":82640,"uid":7790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n當年俾人並稱死火命<br />\n死神？wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 